@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vwcktx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.cos(v0 + 0.68) * v2))
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp(0.49))
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.30) - (tmp + 0.95 + v2 + 0.43)) / ((v0 + 0.44 + v2 + 0.17) * wp.abs(tmp + 0.83)))
    v0 = 0.23
    data[tid] = v0
